From Larry Margolis Subject Re Abortion In Anthony Landreneau writes To Larry Margolis From LM The rape has passed there is nothing that will ever take that LM LM LM But forcing her to remain pregnant continues the violation of LM LM her body for another I see this as being unbelievably LM LM Life is not a violation LM But forcing someone to harbor that life in their body is a Letting a mother force a child from her body in order to end that childs life is the ultimate I happen to take the violation of a person much more seriously than the violation of a mindless clump of cells smaller than my Your mileage may Larry Margolis MARGOLI YKTVMV Bitnet margoli Internet